hadiths[59]{hadithnumber,text}:
6802,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas qabila ukul ke chand log aaey aur Islam qabool kya lekin Madina ki aab w hua unhein muwafiq nahi aai (unke pet phool gaey ( to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke sadqe ke oonton ke rewad mein jayen aur unka peshab aur doodh mila kar piein. unhon-ne iske mutabiq amal kya aur tandurust ho gaey lekin iske baad wo murtad ho gaey aur un oonton ke charwaahon ko qatl karke oont hankaa ley gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki talash mein sawar bhejey aur unhein pakad ke laya gaya phir unke hath paon kaat diye gaey aur unki aankhen phod di gain (kyonke unhon-ne Islami charwaahey ke sath aisa hi bartaw kya tha) aur unke zakhmon par dagh nahi lagwaayaa gaya yahan tak ke wo mar gaey.
6803,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Urainiyon ke) hath paon ( katwaa diye lekin un par dagh nahi lagwaayaa , yahan tak ke wo mar gaey."
6804,"qabila ukul ke kuchh log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas 6 hijri mein aaey aur ye log masjid ke saaybaan mein thahrey . Madina Munawra ki aab w hua unhein muwafiq nahi aai. unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! hamarey liye doodh kahin se muhaiya kara dein, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to mere paas nahi hai. albatta tum log hamarey oonton mein chaley jao . chunanche wo aaey aur unka doodh aur peshab piyaa aur sihat mand ho kar motey taazey ho gaey. phir unhon-ne charwaahey ko qatl kar diya aur oonton ko hankaa ley gaey. itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas faryaadii pahuncha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki talash mein sawar bhejey. abhi dhoop zyada phailii bhi nahi thi ke unhein pakad kar laya gaya phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se salaaiyaan garm ki gain aur unki aankhon mein pher di gain aur unke hath paon kaat diye gaey aur unke ( zakhm se khoon ko rokney ke liye) unhein daaghaa bhi nahi gaya. iske baad wo Harra (Madina ki pathreelii zameen ( mein daal diye gaey, wo pani maangtey they lekin unhein pani nahi diya gaya. yahan tak ke wo mar gaey. abu-Qilaba ne kaha ke ye is wjah se kya gaya tha ke unhon-ne chori ki thi, qatl kya tha aur Allah aur uske rasool se ghaddaaraana ladai ladii thi."
6805,"qabila ukul ya Uraina ke chand log main samajhta hun ukul ka lafz kaha, Madina aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye doodh dene wali oontniyon ka intizam kar diya aur farmaya ke wo oonton ke galle mein jayen aur unka peshab aur doodh piein. chunanche unhon-ne piyaa aur jab wo tandurust ho gaey to charwaahey ko qatl kar diya aur oonton ko hankaa ley gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ye khabar subah ke waqt pahunchi to aap ne unke peechhey sawar daudaaey. abhi dhoop zyada phailii bhi nahi thi ke wo pakad kar laey gaey. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se unke bhi hath paon kaat diye gaey aur unki bhi aankhon mein silai pher di gaee aur unhein Harra mein daal diya gaya. wo pani maangtey they lekin unhein pani nahi diya jata tha. abu-Qilaba ne kaha ke ye wo log they jinhoney chori ki thi, qatl kya tha, eman ke baad kufr ikhtiyar kya tha aur Allah aur uske rasool se ghaddaaraana ladai ladii thi."
6806,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' saat (7) aadmi aisey hain jinhein Allah Taala qiyamat ke din apne arsh ke nichey saaya dega jabke uske arsh ke saaye ke siwa aur koi saaya nahi hoga. aadil haakim, naujawaan jisne Allah ki ibadat mein jawaanii paaii, aisa shakhs jisne Allah ko tanhai mein yad kya aur uski aankhon se aansu nikal padey, wo shakhs jiska dil masjid mein laga rehta hai, wo aadmi jo Allah ke liye mohabbat kartey hain, wo shakhs jisey kisi buland martaba aur khoobsurat aurat ne apni taraf bulaya aur us ne jawab diya ke main Allah se darta hun aur wo shakhs jisne itna posheeda sadqa kya ke uske baaein hath ko bhi pata na chal saka ke daain ne kitna aur kya sadqa kya hai.''"
6807,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne mujhey apne donon paon ke darmyan yani ( sharmgah ( ki aur apne donon jabdon ke darmyan (yani zaban ( ki zamaanat de di to main usey jannat mein janey ka bharosa dilata hoon.''
6808,"main tum se aik aisi hadis bayan karunga ke mere baad koi usey nahi bayan karega. maine ye hadis Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey suna ke qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi ya yun farmaya ke qiyamat ki nishaniyon mein se ye hai ke ilm Deen duniya se uth jaeyga aur jahaalat phail jaeygi, sharab kasrat se pi janey lagegii aur zina phail jaeyga mard kam ho jaeinge aur aurton ki kasarat hogi. haalat yahan tak pahunch jaeygi ke pachaas aurton par aik hi khabar leney wala mard reh jaeyga"
6809,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''banda jab zina karta hai to wo momin nahi rehta . banda jab chori karta hai to wo momin nahi rehta aur banda jab sharab peetaa hai to wo momin nahi rehta aur jab wo qatl nahaq karta hai to wo momin nahi rahtaa. Ikrima ne kaha ke maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke eman us se kis tarah nikal liya jata hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo is tarah aur us waqt aap ne apni ungliyon ko doosrey hath ki ungliyon mein daal kar phir alag kar liya phir agar wo tauba kar leta hai to eman uske paas lot aata hai, is tarah aur aap ne apni ungliyon ko doosrey hath ki ungliyon mein dala."
6810,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''zinaa karne wala jab zina karta hai to wo momin nahi rehta, wo chor jab chori karta hai to wo momin nahi rehta, shraabii jab sharab peetaa hai to wo momin nahi rehta . phir un sab aadmiyon ke liye tauba ka darwaza bahar-haal khula hua hai.''"
6811,"maine puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kon sa gunah sabse bada hai. farmaya ye ke tum Allah ka kisi ko Sharik banaao, halanke usi ne tumhen paida kya hai. maine puchha : iske ba'd? farmaya ye ke tum apni aulad ko us  khatrey (خطرے) se mar dalo ke wo tumharey khaney main tumharey sath Sharik hogi. maine puchha : iske ba'd? farmaya ye ke tum apne padosi ki biwi se zina karo, Yahya ne bayan kya, unse Sufiyan ne bayan kya, unse vaasiil (واصل) ne bayan kya, unse abu-Waeil ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! phir usi hadis ki tarah bayan kya. Amr ne kaha ke phir maine is hadis ka zikr Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi se kya aur unhon-ne ham se ye hadis Sufiyan soury se bayan ki, unse Aa'mash, Mansoor aur vaasiil (واصل) ne, unseunse abu-Waeil (ابوائل) ne aur unse abu-maisraa (ابومیسرہ) ne. Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha ke tum is sanad ko janey bhi do."
6812,jab unhon-ne Juma ke din aurat ko rajm (sangsaar) kya to kaha ke maine iska rajm (sangsaar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat ke mutabiq kya hai.
6813,"kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi ko rajm (sangsaar) kya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, maine puchha : sura Noor se pahley ya iske ba'd? kaha ke ye mujhey malum nahi (naa-maaloom baat ke liye laa-ilmii zahir kar dena kar dena bhi durust hai)."
6814,"qabila Aslam ke aik sahib Maaiz naam ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur kaha ke maine zina kya hai. phir unhon-ne apne zina ka char martaba iqrar kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm diya aur unhein rajm (sangsaar) kya gaya, wo shadi shuda they."
6815,"aik sahib Maaiz bin Malik Aslami Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey, us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein they, unhon-ne aapko awaz di aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! maine zina kar liya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf se munh pher liya. unhon-ne ye baat char baar dohraaii jab char baar unhon-ne us gunah ki apne uper shahadat di to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulaya aur malum farmaya kya tum deewaaney ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke phir kya tum shadi shuda ho? unhon-ne kaha ji haan. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ley jao aur rajm (sangsaar) kar do."
6816,"rajm (sangsaar) karne walon mein, main bhi tha ham ne unhein aabadi se bahar eidgaah ke paas rajm (sangsaar) kya tha jab un par patthar padey to wo bhag padey lekin ham ne unhein Harra ke paas pakda aur rajm (sangsaar) kar diya."
6817,Sad-bin-abi-Waqas aur abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapas mein (eik bachchey Abdur-Rehman naam ke mein) ikhtilaf kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''abd-bin-Zam'a ! bachcha to ley-ley bachcha usi ko milega jiski jouroo ya londi ke pet se wo paida hua aur Sauda ! tum us se parda kya karo.'' imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Quteba ne Leis se is zyada ke sath bayan kya ke zaanii ke hissey mein patthar ki saza hai.
6818,maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ladkaa usi ko milta hai jiski jouroo ya londi ke pet se hua ho aur haram kaar ke liye sirf patthar hain.''
6819,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik Yahudi mard aur aik Yahudi aurat ko laya gaya, jinhoney zina kya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha ke tumhari kitab Taurait mein uski saza kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke hamarey ulma ne (uskii sazaa) chehrey ko siyah karna aur gadhey par ulta sawar karna tajwiz ki hui hai. is par Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! unse Taurait mangwaaiye. jab Taurait laai gaee to unmein se aik ne rajm (sangsaar) wali aayat par apna hath rakh liya aur us se aagey aur peechhey ki aayatein padhney laga. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha ke apna hath hataao (aur jab us ne apna hath hataya to) aayat rajm (sangsaar) uske hath ke nichey thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon ke mutaalliq hukm diya aur unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unhein balaat (masjide-Nabawi ke qareeb aik jagah ( mein rajm (sangsaar) kya gaya. maine dekha ke Yahudi aurat ko mard bachaney ke liye is par jhuk-jhuk padta tha."
6820,qabila Aslam ke aik sahib (maaiz bin Maalik) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur zina ka iqrar kya. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf se apna munh pher liya. phir jab unhon-ne char martaba apne liye gawahi di to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha kya tum deewaaney ho gaey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. phir aap ne puchha kya tumhara nikah ho chuka hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan. chunanche aap ke hukm se unhein eidgaah mein rajm (sangsaar) kya gaya. jab un par patthar padey to wo bhag padey lekin unhein pakad liya gaya aur rajm (sangsaar) kya gaya yahan tak ke wo mar gaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke haq mein kalima khair farmaya aur unka janaaza ada kya aur unki tareef ki jiske wo mustahiq they.
6821,aik sahib ne Ramazan main apni biwi se ham-bistarii kar li aur phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska hukm puchha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tumharey paas koi ghulam hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya do mahiney rozey rakhney ki tum mein taqat nahi ? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par kaha ke phir sath (60) mohtajon ko khana khilaao .
6822,aik sahib Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas masjid mein aaey aur arz kya main to dozakh ka mustahiq ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya baat huii? kaha ke maine apni biwi se Ramazan mein hambistari kar li hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha ke phir sadqa kar. unhon-ne kaha ke mere paas kuchh bhi nahi. phir wo baith gaya aur uske baad aik sahib gadhaa haanktey laey jis par khaney ki cheez rakhi thi. Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya ke mujhey malum nahi ke wo kya cheez thi. (doosri riwayat mein yun hai ke khajoor ladi hui thi) usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya ja raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke aag mein jalney waley sahib kahan hain? wo sahib boley ke main hazir hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ley aur sadqa kar de. unhon-ne puchha kya apne se zyada mohtaaj ko dun? mere ghar walon ke liye to khud koi khaney ki cheez nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum hi kha lo. Abdullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke pehlii hadis zyada waazeh hai jis main (أطعم أهلك) ke alfaz hain.
6823,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas tha ke aik sahib Ka'b-bin-Amr aaey aur kaha : ya Rasulullah! mujh par had (sharaii sazaa) wajib ho gaee hai. aap mujh par had jari keejiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se kuchh nahi poochha. bayan kya ke phir Namaz ka waqt ho gaya aur un sahib ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh chukey to wo phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa kar khadey ho gaey aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! mujh par had wajib ho gaee hai aap kitabullah ke hukm ke mutabiq mujh par had jari kijiye . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke kya tum ne abhi hamarey sath Namaz nahi padhi hai. unhon-ne kaha ke ji . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Allah ne tera gunah maaf kar diya ya farmaya ke teri ghalati ya had (muaaf kar dii).
6824,jab Maaiz bin Malik Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke ghaaliban tu ney bosa diya hoga ya ishara kya hoga ya dekha hoga. unhon-ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya kya phir tu ney ham-bistarii hi kar li hai? is martaba aap ne ishaaroo se kaam nahi liya. bayan kya ke iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm diya.
6825,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik sahib aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt masjid mein baithey huey they. unhon-ne awaz di ya Rasulullah ! maine zina kya hai. khud apne mutaalliq wo keh rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse apna munh pher liya. lekin wo sahib bhi hat kar usi taraf khadey ho gaey jidhar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna munh phera tha aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine zina kya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir apna munh pher liya aur wo bhi dobara us taraf aagey jidhar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna munh phera tha aur is tarah jab us ne char martaba apne gunah ka iqrar kar liya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko bulaya aur puchha kya tum paagal (پاگل) ho? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tum shadi shuda ho? unhon-ne kaha : ji ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke unhein ley jao aur rajm (sangsaar) kar do.
6826,main bhi un logon mein shamil tha jinhoney unhein rajm (sangsaar) kya tha jab un par patthar padey to wo bhaagney lagey. lekin ham ne unhein Harra (Harra Madina ki pathreelii zameen) mein ja liya aur unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya.
6827,main bhi un logon mein shamil tha jinhoney unhein rajm (sangsaar) kya tha jab un par patthar padey to wo bhaagney lagey. lekin ham ne unhein Harra (Harra Madina ki pathreelii zameen) mein ja liya aur unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya.
6828,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas they, to aik sahib khadey huey aur kaha, main aapko Allah ki qism deta hun aap hamarey darmyan Allah ki kitab se faisla karein. is par uska muqabil bhi khada ho gaya aur wo pahley se zyada samajhdaar tha, phir usne kaha ke waqei aap hamarey darmyan kitabullah se hi faisla kijiye aur mujhey bhi guftgu ki ijazat dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho, us shakhs ne kaha ke mera betaa us shakhs ke yahan mazdoorii par kaam karta tha phir us ne uski aurat se zina kar liya, maine iske fidya mein usey sou (100) bakri aur aik khaadim diya, phir maine kuchh ilm walon se puchha to unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke mere ladkey par so kode aur aik saal Shahar Badr honey ki had wajib hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main tumharey darmyan kitabullah hi ke mutabiq faisla karunga . sou (100) bakriyaan aur khaadim tumhen wapas hongey aur tumharey betey ko so kode lagaey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye usey shahar badar kya jaeyga aur aey unnais ! subah ko uski aurat ke paas jana agar wo (zinaa ka ( iqrar kar ley to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do. chunanche wo subah ko uske paas gaey aur us ne iqrar kar liya aur unhon-ne rajm (sangsaar) kar diya. Ali-bin-Abdullaah-madeenii kehtey hain maine Sufiyaan-bin-Ueina se puchha jis shakhs ka betaa tha us ne yun nahi kaha ke un aalimon ne mujh se bayan kya ke terey betey par rajm (sangsaar) hai. unhon-ne kaha ke mujh ko usmein shak hai ke Zohri se maine suna hai ya nahi, isliye maine usko kabhi bayan kya, kabhi nahi bayan kya, balkii khaamoosh raha."
6829,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main darta hun ke kahin zyada waqt guzar jaey aur koi shakhs ye kehney lagey ke kitabullah main to rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm hamein kahin nahi milta aur is tarah wo Allah ke aik fareeza ko chhod kar gumrah hon jisey Allah Taala ne nazil kya hai. aagah ho jao ke rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm us shakhs ke liye farz hai jisne shadi shuda honey ke bawajud zina kya ho basharte ke sahi sharaee gawaahiyon se Sabit ho jaey ya hamal ho ya koi khud iqrar kare. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine isi tarah yad kya tha aagah ho jao ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rajm (sangsaar) kya tha aur aap ke baad ham ne rajm (sangsaar) kya tha."
6830,"mein kai muhajireen ko) Quran Majeed ( padhaayaa karta tha. Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unmein se aik they. abhi main Mina mein unke makan par tha aur wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke aakhiri Haj main (23 hijri ( unke sath they ke wo mere paas lot kar aaey aur kaha ke kash! tum us shakhs ko dekhtey jo aaj ameerul-momineen ke paas aaya tha. usne kaha ke aey ameerul-momineen! kya aap falan sahib se ye poochh-gachh karengey jo ye kehtey hain ke agar umr ka intiqal ho gaya to main falan sahib Talha bin Ubaidullah se bait karunga kyonke Allah ki qism Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baghair sochey samjhey bait to achcha ho gaee aur phir wo mukammal ho gaee thi. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) bahut ghussa huey aur kaha, main inshaAllah Sham ke waqt logon se khitab karunga aur unhein un logon se daraaoonga jo zabardastii se dakhal dr-ma'qoolaat karna chahtey hain. Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke is par maine arz kya : ya ameerul-momineen! aisa na kijiye . Haj ke mausam mein kam samjhii aur burey-bhaley har hi qism ke log jama hain aur jab aap khitab ke liye khadey hongey to aap ke qareeb yahi log zyada hongey aur mujhey dar hai ke aap khadey ho kar koi baat kahein aur wo charon taraf phail jaey, lekin phailaaney waley usey sahi taur par yad na rakh sakengey aur uske ghalat maana pehnaaney lagengey, isliye Madina Munawra pahunchne tak ka intizar kar lijiye kyonke wo hijrat aur sunnat ka maqam hai. wahan aapko khalis deeni samajh-boojh rakhney waley aur sharif log milengey, wahan aap jo kuchh kehna chahtey hain aitimad ke sath hi farma sakengey aur ilm waley aap ki baton ko yad bhi rakhengey aur jo sahi matlab hai wahi bayan karengey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha haan achchha Allah ki qism main Madina Munawra pahunchtey hi sabse pahley logon ko usi mazmoon ka khutba doonga . Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ham Zil-Hijja ke maheene ke aakhir mein Madina Munawra pahunchey . Juma ke din suraj dhaltey hi ham ne (masjide-Nabawii) pahunchne mein jaldi ki aur maine dekha ke Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail mimber ki jad ke paas baithey huey they. main bhi unke paas baith gaya. mera takhna unke takhney se laga hua tha. thodi hi der mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi bahar nikley, jab maine unhein aatey dekha to Saeed bin Zaid-bin-Amr-bin-Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) se maine kaha ke aaj umr (Raziallahu anhu) aisi baat kahengey jo unhon-ne us se pahley khaleefa banaey janey ke baad kabhi nahi kahi thi. lekin unhon-ne usko na maanaa aur kaha ke main to nahi samajhta ke aap koi aisi baat kahengey jo pahley kabhi nahi kahi thi. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) member par baithey aur jab muazzan azan de kar khamosh hua to aap khadey huey aur Allah Taala ki sana uski shaan ke mutabiq bayan karne ke baad farmaya : ammaa ba'd! aaj main tum se aik aisi baat kahunga jiska kehna meri taqdeer mein likha hua tha, mujh ko nahi malum ke shayad meri ye guftgu maut ke qareeb ki aakhiri guftgu ho. to jo koi usey samjhey aur mehfooz rakhey usey chahiye ke is baat ko us jagah tak pahuncha de jahan tak uski sawari usey ley ja sakti hai aur jisey khof ho ke usne baat nahi samjhii hai to uske liye jaaiz nahi hai ke meri taraf ghalat baat mansub kare. bila shubah Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath maboos kya aur aap par kitab nazil ki, kitabullah ki sura mein jo kuchh aap par nazil hua, unmein aayat rajm (sangsaar) bhi thi. ham ne usey padha tha samjha tha aur yad rakha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud (apne zamane mein) rajm (sangsaar) karaya. phir aap ke baad ham ne bhi rajm (sangsaar) kya lekin mujhey dar hai ke agar waqt yun hi aagey badhtaa raha to kahin koi ye na dawa kar baithey ke rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat ham kitabullah mein nahi patey aur is tarah wo us fareeze ko chhod kar gumrah hon jisey Allah Taala ne nazil kya tha. yaqinan rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm kitabullah se us shakhs ke liye Sabit hai jisne shadi honey ke baad zina kya ho. chahe mard hon ya auratein , basharte ke gawahi mukammal ho jaey ya hamal zahir ho ya wo khud iqrar kar ley phir kitabullah ki aayaton mein ham ye bhi padhtey they ke apne haqiqi bap daadon ke siwa dusron ki taraf apne aapko mansub na karo. kyonke ye tumhara kufr aur inkar hai ke tum apne asl bap daadon ke siwa dusron ki taraf apni nisbat karo. haan aur sun lo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya tha ke meri tareef had se badha kar na karna jis tarah Esa ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki had se badha kar ta'reefein ki gain (unko Allah ko betaa bana diya gaya) balke ( mere liye sirf ye kaho ke) mein Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hun aur mujhey ye bhi malum hua hai ke tum mein se kisi ne yun kaha hai ke Allah ki qism agar umr ka intiqal ho gaya to main falan se bait karunga dekho tum mein se kisi ko ye dhokaa na ho ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki bait naagaah hui aur Allah ne naa-gahaanii bait mein jo burai hui hai us se tum ko bachaaey rakha uski wjah ye hui ke tum ko Allah Taala ne uske shar se mehfooz rakha aur tum mein koi shakhs aisa nahi jo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jaisa muttaqii , khuda taras ho. tum mein kon hai jis se milney ke liye oont chillaey jatey hun. dekho khayal rakho koi shakhs kisi se baghair musalmanon ke salaah-mashware aur ittifaq aur ghalba raayon ke baghair bait na karey jo koi aisa karega uska nateeja yahi hoga ke bait karne wala aur bait leney wala donon apni jaan ganwaa dengey aur sun lo bila shubah jis waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ham sabse behtar they albatta Ansar ne hamari mukhalifat ki thi aur wo sab log Saqeefaa-banii-saaida mein jama ho gaey they. isi tarah Ali aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ne bhi hamari mukhalifat ki thi aur baqi muhajireen Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jama ho gaey they. us waqt maine Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aey Abu-Bakar ! hamein apne un Ansari bhaiyon ke paas ley chaliye . chunanche ham unse mulaqat ke irade se chal padey . jab ham unke qareeb pahunchey to hamari , unhein ke 2 nek logon se mulaqat hui aur unhon-ne ham se bayan kya ke Ansari aadmiyon ne ye baat thahraaii hai ke) Sad-bin-Ubada ko khaleefa banaaein) aur unhon-ne poochha. hazraat muhajireen aap log kahan ja rahe hain. ham ne kaha ke ham apne un Ansari bhaiyon ke paas ja rahe hain. unhon-ne kaha ke aap log hargiz wahan na jayen balke khud jo karna hai kar dalo lekin maine kaha ke b-khudaa ham zaroor jaengey. chunanche ham aagey badhey aur Ansar ke paas Saqeefaa-banii-saaida mein pahunchey majlis mein aik sahib (sardaar khazraj) chadar apne sarey jism par lapetey darmyan mein baithey they. maine puchha ke ye kon sahib hain to logon ne bataya ke Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) hain. maine puchha ke unhein kya ho gaya hai? logon ne bataya ke bukhar aa raha hai. phir hamarey thodi der tak baithney ke baad unke khateeb ne kalima shahadat padha aur Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq tareef ki. phir kaha : ammaa ba'd! ham Allah ke Deen ke madadgaar ( Ansar (aur Islam ke lashkar hain aur tum aey giroh muhajireen ! kam tadaad mein ho. tumhari ye thodi si tadaad apni qaum Quraish se nikal kar ham logon mein aa rahe ho. tum log ye chahtey ho ke hamein jad se ukhaad dalo aur ham ko khilafat se mahroom karke aap khaleefa bin baitho, ye kabhi nahi ho sakta. jab wo khutba pura kar chukey to maine bolnaa chaha. maine aik umda taqreer apne zahan mein tarteeb de rakhi thi. meri badi khahish thi ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke baat karne se pahley hi main usko shuru kar dun aur Ansar ki taqreer se jo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghussa paida hua hai usko door kar dun jab maine baat karni chahi to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha zara thehro maine unko naraz karna bura jaanaa. aakhir unhon-ne hi taqreer shuru ki aur Allah ki qism ! wo mujh se zyada aqlmand aur mujh se zyada sanjeeda aur mateen they. maine jo taqreer apne dil mein soch li thi usmein se unhon-ne koi baat nahi chhodii. faurii taur par wahi kahi balke us se bhi behtar phir wo khamosh ho gaey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taqreer ka khulaasa ye tha ke Ansari bhaiyo ! tum ne jo apni fazeelat aur buzurgi bayan ki hai wo sab durust hai aur tum beshak uske haqdaar ho magar khilafat Quraish ke siwa aur kisi khandan walon ke liye nahi ho sakti . kyonke Quraish azrooye nasb aur azrooye khandan tamam Arab qaumon mein badh chadh kar hain ab tum log aisa karo ke un 2 aadmiyon mein se kisi se bait kar lo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mera aur abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah ka hath thaamaa wo hamarey beech mein baithey huey they, is saari guftgu mein sirf yahi aik baat mujh se mere siwa hui. Allah ki qism main aagey kar diya jata aur be-gunaah meri gardan mar di jati to ye mujhey us se zyada pasand tha ke mujhey aik aisi qaum ka ameer banaya jata jis mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khud maujood hon. mera ab tak yahi khayal hai ye aur baat hai ke waqt par nafs mujhey bahkaa de aur main koi doosra khayal karun jo ab nahi karna. phir Ansar mein se aik kehney wala hubaab bin munzir yun kehney laga suno-suno main aik lakdi hun ke jis se oont apna badan ragad kar khujlii ki takleef rafa' kartey hain aur main wo baadh hun jo darakhton ke ird-gird hifazat ke liye lagai jati hai. main aik umda tadbeer bataataa hun aisa karo 2 khaleefa rahen (donon mil kar kaam karein) aik hamari qaum ka aur aik Quraish walon kaa. muhajireen qaum ka ab khub shor-ghul honey laga koi kuchh kehta koi kuchh kehta . main dar gaya ke kahin musalmanon mein phoot na pad jaey aakhir main keh utha abu-Bakar! apna hath badhaao, unhon-ne hath badhaya maine unse bait ki aur muhajireen jitney wahan maujood they unhon-ne bhi bait kar li phir ansaariyon ne bhi bait kar li (chalo jhagdaa tamam hua jo manzoor ilahi tha wahi zahir hua) iske baad ham Sad-bin-Ubada ki taraf badhey ( unhon-ne bait nahi ki) aik shakhs Ansar mein se kehney laga : bhaiyo ! bechaarey Sad-bin-Ubada ka tum ne khoon kar dala. maine kaha Allah uska khoon karega . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us khutbey mein ye bhi farmaya us waqt ham ko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat se zyada koi cheez zaroori malum nahi hoti kyonke ham ko dar paida hua kahin aisa na ho ham logon se juda rahen aur abhi unhon-ne kisi se bait na ki ho wo kisi aur shakhs se bait kar baithein tab 2 Suraton se khali nahi hota ya to ham bhi jabran usi se bait kar letey ya logon ki mukhalifat kartey to aapas mein fasaad paida hota ( phoot pad jati ( dekho phir yahi kehta hun jo shakhs kisi se bin sochey samjhey , bin salaah w mashwara bait kar ley to doosrey log bait karne waley ki pairwi na karey, na uski jis se bait ki gaee hai kyonke wo donon apni jaan ginwaaeingey."
6831,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un logon ke barey mein hukm de rahe they jo ghair shadi shuda hon aur zina kya ho ke so kode maarey jayen aur saal bhar ke liye jilaa watan kar diya jaey."
6832,umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne jilaa watan kya tha phir yahi tariqa qaaim ho gaya.
6833,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisey shakhs ke barey mein jisne zina kya tha aur wo ghair shadi shuda tha, had qaaim karne ke sath aik saal tak Shahar se bahar karne ka faisla kya tha."
6834,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un mardon par laanat ki hai jo mukhannas bantey hain aur un aurton par laanat ki hai jo mard bantii hain aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein apne gharon se nikal do aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne falan ko ghar se nikala tha aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne falan ko nikala tha.
6835,"aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! hamarey darmyan kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dein. is par doosrey ne khadey ho kar kaha ke unhon-ne sahi kaha ya Rasulullah ! unka kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla karein, mera ladka unke yahan mazdoor tha aur phir us ne unki biwi ke sath zina kar liya. logon ne mujhey bataya ke mere ladkey ko rajm (sangsaar) kya jaeyga chunanche maine so bakriyon aur aik kaneez ka fidya diya. phir maine ahale-ilm se puchha to unka khayal hai ke mere ladkey par so kode aur aik saal ki jilaa watanii lazimi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main tum donon ka faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq karunga. bakriyan aur kaneez tumhen wapas milengii aur tumharey ladkey ko so kode aur aik saal ki jilaa watanii ki saza milegii aur Anees ! subah us aurat ke paas jao (aur agar wo iqrar karey to) usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do. chunanche unhon-ne usey rajm (sangsaar) kya. (wo aurat kahin aur jagah thi) aap ne usey rajm (sangsaar) karne ke liye Anees ko bheja usi se baab ka matlab nikla . qastalaanii ne kaha ke aap ne jo Anees ko fareeq saanii ki joru ke paas bheja wo zina ki had maarney ke liye nahi bheja kyonke zina ki had lagaaney ke liye tajassus karna ya dhoondhnaa bhi durust nahi hai agar koi khud aa kar bhi zina ka iqrar karey uske liye bhi chhaanbeen karna mustahab hai, yani yun kehna ke shayad tu ney bosa diya hoga ya chhuaa hoga balke aap ne Anees ko sirf isliye bheja ke us aurat ko khabar kar dein ke falan shakhs ne tujh par zina ki tohmat lagai hai. ab wo hade-qazaf ka mutalba karti hai ya maaf karti hai. jab Anees uske paas pahunchey to us aurat ne saaf taur par zina qabool kya. is qabool karney par Anees (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko had lagai aur rajm (sangsaar) kya."
6836,"eik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! hamarey darmyan kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dein. is par doosrey ne khadey ho kar kaha ke unhon-ne sahi kaha ya Rasulullah ! unka kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla karein, mera ladka unke yahan mazdoor tha aur phir us ne unki biwi ke sath zina kar liya. logon ne mujhey bataya ke mere ladkey ko rajm (sangsaar) kya jaeyga chunanche maine so bakriyon aur aik kaneez ka fidya diya. phir maine ahale-ilm se puchha to unka khayal hai ke mere ladkey par so kode aur aik saal ki jilaa watanii lazimi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main tum donon ka faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq karunga. bakriyan aur kaneez tumhen wapas milengii aur tumharey ladkey ko so kode aur aik saal ki jilaa watanii ki saza milegii aur Anees ! subah us aurat ke paas jao (aur agar wo iqrar karey to) usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do. chunanche unhon-ne usey rajm (sangsaar) kya. (wo aurat kahin aur jagah thi) aap ne usey rajm (sangsaar) karne ke liye Anees ko bheja usi se baab ka matlab nikla . qastalaanii ne kaha ke aap ne jo Anees ko fareeq saanii ki joru ke paas bheja wo zina ki had maarney ke liye nahi bheja kyonke zina ki had lagaaney ke liye tajassus karna ya dhoondhnaa bhi durust nahi hai agar koi khud aa kar bhi zina ka iqrar karey uske liye bhi chhaanbeen karna mustahab hai, yani yun kehna ke shayad tu ney bosa diya hoga ya chhuaa hoga balke aap ne Anees ko sirf isliye bheja ke us aurat ko khabar kar dein ke falan shakhs ne tujh par zina ki tohmat lagai hai. ab wo hade-qazaf ka mutalba karti hai ya maaf karti hai. jab Anees uske paas pahunchey to us aurat ne saaf taur par zina qabool kya. is qabool karney par Anees (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko had lagai aur rajm (sangsaar) kya."
6837,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us kaneez ke mutaalliq puchha gaya jo ghair shadi shuda ho aur zina kara liya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo zina kiraaey to usey kode maaro, agar phir zina kiraaey to phir kode maaro, agar phir zina kiraaey to phir kode maaro aur usey bech dalo chahe aik rassii hi qeemat mein miley. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke mujhey yaqin nahi ke teesri martaba (kode lagaaney ke hukm (ke baad ye farmaya ya chothi martaba ke baad ."
6838,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us kaneez ke mutaalliq puchha gaya jo ghair shadi shuda ho aur zina kara liya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo zina kiraaey to usey kode maaro , agar phir zina kiraaey to phir kode maaro, agar phir zina kiraaey to phir kode maaro aur usey bech dalo chahe aik rassii hi qeemat mein miley. ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya ke mujhey yaqin nahi ke teesri martaba ( kode lagaaney ke hukm (ke baad ye farmaya ya chothi martaba ke baad ."
6839,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar kaneez zina kiraaey aur uska zina khul jaey to usey kode maarney chaahiyein lekin laanat malaamat na karni chahiye phir agar wo dobara zina karey to phir chahiye ke kode maarey lekin malaamat na karey phir agar teesri martaba zina kiraaey to bech de chahe baalon ki aik rassii hi qeemat par ho. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ismail bin Umayya ne Saeed se ki, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
6840,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rajm (sangsaar) kya tha, maine puchha sura Noor se pahley ya iske ba'd, unhon-ne batlaya ke mujhey malum nahi. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ali-bin-mus'hir, Khalid-bin-Abdullaah al-mahaarabi aur Ubaida-bin-Humaid ne Shebani se ki hai aur kuchh ne (sura Noor ke bajaey) sura Mayeda ka zikr kya hai lekin pehli riwayat sahi hai."
6841,Yahudi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha ke unmein se aik mard aur aik aurat ne zinaakaarii ki hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha ke Taurait mein rajm (sangsaar) ke mutaalliq kya hukm hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ham unhein ruswa kartey hain aur kode lagaatey hain. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke tum jhootey ho usmein rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm maujood hai. chunanche wo Taurait laey aur khola . lekin unke aik shakhs ne apna hath aayate-rajm (sangsaar) par rakh diya aur us se pahley aur baad ka hissa padh diya. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha ke apna hath uthaao. us ne apna hath uthaya to iske nichey rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat maujood thi. phir unhon-ne kaha : aey Muhammad! aap ne sach farmaya ke usmein rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat maujood hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur donon rajm (sangsaar) kiye gaey. maine dekha ke mard aurat ko pattharon se bachaney ki koshish main is par jhukaa raha tha.
6842,"2 aadmi apna muqaddima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laey aur unmein se aik ne kaha ke hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dijiye aur doosrey ne jo zyada samajhdaar they kaha ke ji haan ya Rasulullah! hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dijiye aur mujhey arz karne ki ijazat dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho, unhon-ne kaha ke mera betaa un sahib ke yahan mazdoor tha. Malik ne bayan kya ke) Aseef ( mazdoor ko kehtey hain aur us ne unki biwi ke sath zina kar liya. logon ne mujh se kaha ke mere betey ki saza rajm (sangsaar) hai. chunanche maine iske fidye mein so bakriyan aur aik londi de di phir jab maine ilm walon se puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke mere ladkey ki saza so kode aur aik saal ke liye mulk badr karna hai. rajm (sangsaar) to sirf us aurat ko kya jaeyga isliye ke wo shadi shuda hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. tumhara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq karunga. tumhari bakriyan aur tumhari londi tumhen wapas hain phir unke betey ko so kode lagwaaey aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr kya aur Anees Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm farmaya ke us mazkura (uper zikr) aurat ke paas jayen agar wo iqrar kar ley to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar dein chunanche us ne iqrar kya aur wo rajm (sangsaar) kar di gaee."
6843,"2 aadmi apna muqaddima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laey aur unmein se aik ne kaha ke hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dijiye aur doosrey ne jo zyada samajhdaar they kaha ke ji haan ya Rasulullah! hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dijiye aur mujhey arz karne ki ijazat dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho, unhon-ne kaha ke mera betaa un sahib ke yahan mazdoor tha. Malik ne bayan kya ke) Aseef ( mazdoor ko kehtey hain aur us ne unki biwi ke sath zina kar liya. logon ne mujh se kaha ke mere betey ki saza rajm (sangsaar) hai. chunanche maine iske fidye mein so bakriyan aur aik londi de di phir jab maine ilm walon se puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke mere ladkey ki saza so kode aur aik saal ke liye mulk badr karna hai. rajm (sangsaar) to sirf us aurat ko kya jaeyga isliye ke wo shadi shuda hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. tumhara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq karunga. tumhari bakriyan aur tumhari londi tumhen wapas hain phir unke betey ko so kode lagwaaey aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr kya aur Anees Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm farmaya ke us mazkura (uper zikr) aurat ke paas jayen agar wo iqrar kar ley to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar dein chunanche us ne iqrar kya aur wo rajm (sangsaar) kar di gaii."
6844,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tumhari wjah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur sab logon ko rukna padaa jabke yahan pani bhi nahi hai. chunanche wo mujh par sakht naraz huey aur apne hath se meri kokh mein mukkaa maarney lagey magar maine apne jism mein kisi qism ki harkat isliye nahi honey di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaraam farma rahe they. phir Allah Taala ne tayammum ki aayat nazil ki.
6845,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur zor se mere aik sakht ghoonsaa lagaya aur kaha tu ney aik haar ke liye sab logon ko rok diya. main us se marney ke qareeb ho gaee is qadr mujh ko dard hua lekin kya kar sakti thi kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar Mubarak meri raan par tha. ( لكز (aur ( وكز (ke aik hi mana hain.
6846,Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar main apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko dekh loon to seedhi talwaar ki dhaar se usey mar daalun . ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tumhen Sad ki ghairat par hairat hai. main unse bhi badh kar ghairat mand hun aur Allah mujh se bhi zyada ghairat mand hai.
6847,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik dehati aaya aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! meri biwi ne kala ladka janaa hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poochha, tumharey paas oont hain? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha unke rang kaisey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke surkh . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha unmein koi khaakii rang ka bhi hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha phir ye kahan se aa gaya? unhon-ne kaha mera khayal hai ke kisi rag ne ye rang kheench liya jiski wjah se aisa oont paida hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aisa bhi mumkin hai ke terey betey ka rang bhi kisi rag ne kheench liya ho."
6848,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ki hadon mein kisi muqarrara had ke siwa kisi aur saza mein das kode se zyada bataur saza na maarey jaaein. ''
6849,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ki tay ki hui sazaaon mein se se kisi had ke siwa mujrim ko das kode se zyada ki saza na di jaaey.''
6850,"main Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ke paas betha hua tha ke Abdur-Rehman bin Jaabir aaey aur Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se bayan kya phir Sulaiman-bin-Yasar hamari taraf mutwajjeh huey aur unhon-ne kaha ke mujh se Abdur-Rehman bin Jaabir ne bayan kya hai ke unse unke walid ne bayan kya aur unhon-ne abu-Barda Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hudood Allah main se kisi had ke siwa kisi saza mein das kode se zyada ki saza na do."
6851,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wisaal (musalsal iftaar ke baghair kai din ke rozey rakhney ( se mana farmaya to kuchh sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap khud to wisaal kartey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se kon mujh jaisa hai? mera to haal ye hai ke mujhey mera rab khilata hai aur pilaataa hai lekin wisaal karne se sahaba nahi rukey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath aik din ke baad doosrey din ka wisaal kya phir iske baad logon ne chaand dekh liya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ( eid ka ( chaand na dikhai deta to main aur wisaal karta. ye aap ne tanbeeh ke taur par farmaya tha kyonke wo wisaal karne par israar kar rahey they. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Shuaib , Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Yunus ne Zohri se ki hai aur Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid Fahmii ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Shahab ne, unse Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya."
6852,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane main is par mar padtii ke jab ghalle ke dher yun hi khareedein, bin naapey aur toley usko usi jagah doosrey ke hath bech daalein haan wo ghalla utha kar apne thikaaney ley jayen phir bechein to kuchh saza na hoti."
6853,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne zaatii maamle mein kabhi kisi se badla nahi liya haan jab Allah ki qaaim ki hui had ko todaa jata to aap phir badla letey they.
6854,"maine 2 liaan karne waley miyan biwi ko dekha tha. us waqt meri umr pandarah saal thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ke darmyan judai kara di thi. shauhar ne kaha tha ke agar ab bhi main (apni biwi ko) apne sath rakhoon to iska matlab ye hai ke main jhoota hun. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine Zohri se ye riwayat mehfooz rakhi hai ke ''agar us aurat ke aisa bachcha paida hua to shauhar sachcha hai aur agar uske aisaa-aisaa bachcha paida hua jaisey chhipkalii hoti hai to shauhar jhoota hai.'' aur maine Zohri se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke us aurat ne us aadmi ke ham-shakl bachcha janaa jo meri tarah ka tha."
6855,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne 2 liaan karne walon ka zikr kya to Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye wahi thi jiske mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar main kisi aurat ko bila gawahi rajm (sangsaar) kar sakta (to usey zaroor kartaa) Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi ye wo aurat thi jo ( fisq w fujoor ( zahir kya karti thi.
6856,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein liaan ka zikr aaya to Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par aik baat kahi phir wo wapas aaey. iske baad unki qaum ke aik sahib ye shikayat lekar unke paas aaey ke unhon-ne apni biwi ke sath ghair mard ko dekha hai. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke main apni is baat ki wjah se aazmaish mein daala gaya hun. phir aap un sahib ko lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein tashrif laey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski itlaa di jis haalat mein unhon-ne apni biwi ko paya. wo sahib zard rang , kam gosht , seedhey baalon waley they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Allah ! us mamla ko zahir kar de. chunanche us aurat ke yahan usi shakhs ki shakl ka bachcha paida hua jiske mutaalliq shauhar ne kaha tha ke usey unhon-ne apni biwi ke sath dekha hai phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ke darmyan liaan karaya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se majlis mein aik sahib ne kaha ke ye wahi tha jiske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar main kisi ko bila gawahi ke rajm (sangsaar) kar sakta to usey rajm (sangsaar) karta. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi ye to wo aurat thi jo Islam laney ke baad buraaiyaan ea'laaniya karti thi."
6857,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''saat (7) halaak karney waaley gunahon se bacho . sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! wo kya kya hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke sath shirk karnaa, jaadoo karnaa, nahaq kisi ki jaan lena jo Allah ne haram kya hai, sood khana , yateem ka maal khana , jang ke din peeth phernaa aur paak daman ghaafil momin aurton ko tohmat lagaanaa .''"
6858,"jisne apne ghulam par tohmat lagai halanke ghulam us tohmat se barii tha to qiyamat ke din usey kode lagaey jaeinge , siwa iske ke uski baat sahi ho."
6859,"aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha ke main aapko Allah ki qism deta hun aap hamarey darmyan kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dein. is par fareeq mukhalif khada hua, ye zyada samajhdaar tha aur kaha ke unhon-ne sach kaha, hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kijiye aur ya Rasulullah ! mujhey ( guftgu ki) ijazat dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kahiye. unhon-ne kaha ke mera ladka inke yahan mazdoorii karta tha phir us ne inkii biwi ke sath zina kar liya. maine iske fidya mein aik so bakriyan aur aik khaadim diya phir maine ahale-ilm se puchha to unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke mere betey ko so kode aur aik saal jilaa watanii ki saza milnii chahiye aur iski biwi ko rajm (sangsaar) kya jaeyga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, main tumhara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq hi karunga. so bakriyan aur khaadim tumhen wapas milengey aur tumharey betey ko so kode aur aik saal jilaa watanii ki saza di jaeygi aur aey Anees us aurat ke paas subah jana aur us se poochhna agar wo zina ka iqrar kar ley to usey rajm (sangsaar) karnaa, us aurat ne iqrar kar liya aur wo rajm (sangsaar) kar di gaee."
6860,"eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha ke main aapko Allah ki qism deta hun aap hamarey darmyan kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dein. is par fareeq mukhalif khada hua, ye zyada samajhdaar tha aur kaha ke unhon-ne sach kaha, hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kijiye aur ya Rasulullah ! mujhey ( guftgu ki) ijazat dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kahiye. unhon-ne kaha ke mera ladka inke yahan mazdoorii karta tha phir us ne inkii biwi ke sath zina kar liya. maine iske fidya mein aik so bakriyan aur aik khaadim diya phir maine ahale-ilm se puchha to unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke mere betey ko so kode aur aik saal jilaa watanii ki saza milnii chahiye aur iski biwi ko rajm (sangsaar) kya jaeyga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, main tumhara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq hi karunga. so bakriyan aur khaadim tumhen wapas milengey aur tumharey betey ko so kode aur aik saal jilaa watanii ki saza di jaeygi aur aey Anees us aurat ke paas subah jana aur us se poochhna agar wo zina ka iqrar kar ley to usey rajm (sangsaar) karnaa, us aurat ne iqrar kar liya aur wo rajm (sangsaar) kar di gaii."
